channel.description:
Hollywire TV is a destination for all things trending in entertainment and pop culture. Host Chelsea Briggs and the Hollywire team stay on the pulse of the trends to deliver a fresh, quirky take on the world of entertainment. 

The channel features a daily news show, red carpet interviews, in-studio chats with musicians, and weekly shows about music, style and the ridiculousness of Hollywood.

Press Inquiries: hollywiremedia [at] hollywire [dot] com | Business Inquiries: business [at] hollywire [dot] com
